  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate the feasibility and advantages of using pressurized perfluorocarbon liquid
      (PCL) perfusion to remove vitreous during suction-cutting 23 GA vitrectomy using a dual,
      dynamic drive (3D)technology, in complicated retinal detachment surgeries.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
